        <p style="font-size:14.5px;line-height:1.7;color:#555;margin:0;">Swapping an undersized or aging basement window for a properly sized egress unit, common in Waverly's older farmhouse-style homes near the town center. Details on <a href="/egress-window-replacement-lincoln/">egress window replacement</a>.</p>
