    <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:16px;">
      <div style="background:#fff;border:1px solid #e3ded4;border-radius:8px;padding:24px 28px;">
        <h3 style="font-family:'Nunito Sans',sans-serif;font-size:18px;font-weight:800;color:#0A3D5C;margin:0 0 10px;">Do newer homes in Waverly still need egress windows for basement bedrooms?</h3>
        <p style="font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;color:#555;margin:0;">Yes. Even in newer construction, the basement windows installed by the builder were sized for an unfinished space, not a bedroom. Once you frame in a bedroom, code requires a proper egress window and well, so an inspection can pass.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="background:#fff;border:1px solid #e3ded4;border-radius:8px;padding:24px 28px;">
        <h3 style="font-family:'Nunito Sans',sans-serif;font-size:18px;font-weight:800;color:#0A3D5C;margin:0 0 10px;">How long does egress window installation take in Waverly?</h3>
        <p style="font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;color:#555;margin:0;">Most single-window installations take one to two days from cut-in to window well backfill, depending on your foundation type and soil conditions. We'll give you a specific timeline during your free estimate.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="background:#fff;border:1px solid #e3ded4;border-radius:8px;padding:24px 28px;">
        <h3 style="font-family:'Nunito Sans',sans-serif;font-size:18px;font-weight:800;color:#0A3D5C;margin:0 0 10px;">Does Lincoln Egress Windows handle permits for Waverly jobs?</h3>
        <p style="font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;color:#555;margin:0;">Yes. Waverly falls under Lancaster County code requirements, the same ones we work with on jobs throughout Lincoln, so we handle the permitting and coordinate the inspection for you.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="background:#fff;border:1px solid #e3ded4;border-radius:8px;padding:24px 28px;">
        <h3 style="font-family:'Nunito Sans',sans-serif;font-size:18px;font-weight:800;color:#0A3D5C;margin:0 0 10px;">What does an egress window cost for a typical Waverly basement?</h3>
        <p style="font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;color:#555;margin:0;">Cost depends on your foundation depth, well material, and whether we're cutting a new opening or replacing an existing window. We provide a free written estimate for every Waverly home, and you can see typical ranges on our <a href="/egress-window-cost/">egress window cost</a> page.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
